 based in Rawalpindi, Pakistan, I have had the opportunity to work on a variety of projects using different technologies and frameworks. I've always enjoyed helping others and sharing what I know, so starting a blog seemed like a natural next step."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"what-you-can-expect"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What You Can Expect"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"On this blog, I'll be covering a range of topics related to web development, database management, DevOps, and cloud computing. I'll also share insights into freelancing and remote work, project management strategies, and my contributions to open-source projects."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"lets-connect"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Let's Connect"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you're interested in these topics, I encourage you to check out my "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/","rel":["noopener","noreferer"],"target":"_blank"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub profile"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to see my latest projects and contributions. Let's embark on this journey together – coding, learning, and growing as a community."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Thank you for visiting, and I look forward to sharing more with you soon!"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":3,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:blog:1-my-first-blog-post.md","_source":"content","_file":"blog/1-my-first-blog-post.md","_stem":"blog/1-my-first-blog-post","_extension":"md"},{"_path":"/blog/2-my-vscode-setup","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"My VSCode Setup | Blog","description":"Explore my minimalist VSCode setup featuring the Minimal Mist theme and settings for a clean, distraction-free coding environment.","headline":"My VSCode Setup","abstract":"Discover how the Minimal Mist theme and custom VSCode settings create a clean and focused coding environment.","date":"2024-07-17T12:00:00","dateUpdated":"","author":"Muhammad Ubaid Raza","authorUrl":"/","socialImage":{"src":"/img/blog/2-my-vscode-setup/typescript-dark.png","mime":"png","alt":"Workplace Screenshot","width":1200,"height":630},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"my-vscode-setup"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My VSCode Setup"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hello, fellow developers! I’m Muhammad Ubaid Raza, and I want to share my latest VSCode setup with you. I've crafted this environment to be as minimalist and distraction-free as possible, and I call it Minimal Mist. This theme and setup have greatly enhanced my coding experience, and I hope it can do the same for you."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You can install this theme from VsCode marketplace: [Minimal Mist](Minimal Mist - Visual Studio Marketplace)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"features-of-minimal-mist"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Features of Minimal Mist"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"subtle-background"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Subtle Background"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I chose a soft and soothing background color "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"#f6f5f0"}]},{"type":"text","value":". This subtle hue reduces eye strain and creates a calm coding environment, perfect for long coding sessions."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"shadow-free-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shadow-Free Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In my quest for a cleaner interface, I disabled shadows. This makes the interface feel lighter and less cluttered, allowing me to focus more on my code."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"streamlined-borders"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Streamlined Borders"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Borders can often add unnecessary visual noise, so I simplified, minimized, or removed them. This provides a clean and focused workspace that helps keep distractions at bay."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"clean-look"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Clean Look"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Overall, the goal is a refined, distraction-free interface that lets me concentrate on what matters most - the code."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"unified-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unified Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The dark theme maintains the same streamlined, shadow-free design and simplified borders for a cohesive look."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Minimal Mist, both in light and dark variants, is perfect for developers who value a clean, minimalist aesthetic."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"preview"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Preview"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Here’s a preview of what you can expect:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"typescript"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Typescript"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"Typescript Light","src":"/img/blog/2-my-vscode-setup/typescript-light.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"my-vscode-settings"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My VsCode Settings"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{}